Struck by an enemys arrow, the powerless Prince Davey ORowane falls into a coma. His soul travels to a place where the greatest of the great gatherthe honorable Hall of Heroes. There a thousand years pass as Davey undergoes excruciating training under their watchful eyes to become a hero too strong for his own good. Now back to his timeline and his kingdom, hes wide awake and the enemies hiding in the kings court better be prepared. The prince they had dismissed is now their biggest threat!
(Source: Tapas)
